    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Analyze customer feedback with Google Drive and Jira 24/7\n\n**Pattern:** Survey & Feedback · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nAnalyze customer feedback with Google Drive and Jira 24/7. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual escalation is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Stamp & Shape Ticket → Payload Valid? → Detect Sentiment → Escalate Negative — Microsoft Teams → Open Jira Ticket → Collect All Outcomes → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to survey & feedback without manual effort\n- Anyone automating escalation in customer support\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Improves response time\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Scales without extra headcount\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Anthropic API key; Google OAuth2 / service account; Jira credentials; Microsoft OAuth2; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
      "id": "dcaadd1e-e45e-ef6f-44c2-42a9bb2f84f6",
      "name": "📘 Workflow Overview"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
